    Show the products accepted by the services

    Source: R/connections.R
    rsat_products.Rd

    Show the products accepted by the services

    Usage

    rsat_products(...)

# S4 method for ANY
rsat_products()

    Arguments

    ...

    additional arguments.

    Value

    prints a list of products

    Examples

    rsat_products()
